{"TopicId":207439,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Increase max mass","CreatedByName":"lvcastro","CreatedById":220491,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-27T20:31:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"lvcastro","CreatedById":220491,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-27T20:31:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow could I increase the max mass allowed on a rocket?\u003Cbr\u003E\nOn begin I can build a rocket with max 18T.\u003Cbr\u003E\nI would like to increase it to build biggest rockets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-27T20:42:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re playing a campaign save, which it sounds like you are, you will need to spend money to upgrade the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E and launch pad to get bigger rockets flying.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, welcome to the forum. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lvcastro","CreatedById":220491,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-27T20:53:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224107647\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207439\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221648413731\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re playing a campaign save, which it sounds like you are, you will need to spend money to upgrade the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E and launch pad to get bigger rockets flying.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, welcome to the forum. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you.\u003Cbr\u003E\nI found this same answer on forum, but I don\u0027t realize how to do it.\u003Cbr\u003E\nCould you explain me better? I mean, what is the build I need click to make this upgrade?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-27T21:39:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpgrade the Launchpad to increase max mass\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpgrade the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to increase the part count.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224107655\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207439\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221648414400\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022220491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lvcastro\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n52 minutes ago, lvcastro said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you.\u003Cbr\u003E\nI found this same answer on forum, but I don\u0027t realize how to do it.\u003Cbr\u003E\nCould you explain me better? I mean, what is the build I need click to make this upgrade?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou will need to right-click on the building to open the upgrade menu, before you go in the building. Then hover over the upgrade button to see what it changes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-03-27T21:47:56Z\u0022 title=\u002203/27/2022 09:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 27, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by StrandedonEarth\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lvcastro","CreatedById":220491,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-03-27T22:20:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224107677\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207439\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221648417146\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/27/2022 at 6:39 PM, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpgrade the Launchpad to increase max mass\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpgrade the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to increase the part count.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou will need to right-click on the building to open the upgrade menu, before you go in the building. Then hover over the upgrade button to see what it changes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will try this.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThank you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u00